"use client" import { Link, useNavigate } from "react-router-dom" import { useAuth } from "../contexts/AuthContext" function Navbar() { const { currentUser, logout } = useAuth() const navigate = useNavigate() const handleLogout = () => { logout() navigate("/login") } return (
UK University Finder
{currentUser ? ( <> Home Find Universities Bookmarks Questions
Profile
) : ( <> Login Register )}
) } export default Navbar
